Package networkHandler

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphProperty<T>
    Interface for calculations of properties of a Graph.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BetweennessCentralityMeasure
    This class is responsible for calculating the Betweenness Centrality Measure of a Node in a Graph with help of a provided ShortestPathList.
    BetweennessCentralityMeasureList
    This class is responsible for managing calculations of a single or multiple BetweennessCentralityMeasures of a given Graph.
    CommandLineReader
    This class implements a parser for command line arguments.
    CommandLineWriter
    This class is responsible for calling printing methods of different GraphPropertys according to the flags set in a given CommandLineReader.
    Connectivity
    This class is responsible for calculating whether a Graph is connected or not, using the Depth First Search Algorithm
    Diameter
    This class is responsible for the calculation of the Diameter of a Graph given a ShortestPathList and its Connectivity.
    Edge
    This class represents an Edge between two Nodes of a Graph.
    Graph
    Class that represents a Graph.
    GraphHandler
    This class is responsible for managing all from GraphProperty derived classes and initiates their calculation on a Graph, which is handled in this class as well.
    GraphmlReader
    Class is used to handle the provided graphml file from the user.
    GraphmlWriter
    This class implements the output of all calculations done over a graph into a new file.
    Main
    The Main class is responsible for correct initialization of all other classes in the correct Order.
    MinimumSpanningTree
    Responsible for calculation of a Minimum Spanning Tree for a Graph.
    Node
    This class represents a node in a Graph.
    Path
    This class represents a path of Nodes in a Graph.
    ShortestPathList
    This class is responsible to calculate shortest Paths between Nodes in a given Graph.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoArgumentException
    This class implements an exception for missing arguments.
